{"tid":478638,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「有鳩的妖魔」日本超級美女？　真相係40歲偽娘大叔！","createTime":"2017-11-24T09:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T11:39:22.000Z","uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e244f45b263118bf8660ed1dfaefe959f4e67d9b","tid":478638,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"日本歌手谷琢磨，乍看是一位樣子甜美、正值年輕的少女，但事實上卻讓人大吃一驚，皆因「他」是一名年屆40、已婚並育有一名女兒的叔叔。這位單憑外貌定會讓人誤會性別的「偽娘」，近日在其Twitter上抱着女兒合照，相中卻以可愛字體寫上「祝父親40歲生日快樂」，讓發現真相的網民不禁高呼「詐騙」，一時間成為網絡熱話。 <br />\n<br />\n谷琢磨於上周五（17日）剛好40歲，故於Twitter上公布與女兒的合照，並留言指本年喜獲愛女、成為父親，是人生中的一個里程碑。不過，其附上的照片才是眾人的熱議對象，皆因谷琢磨綁起雙馬尾、身穿蕾絲花邊裙裝，令人懷疑「他」是媽媽才對。該張相片目前已獲逾1.6萬人轉推，逾2萬人讚好。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，谷琢磨的身高僅有162cm，體重更只得47公斤，身型看起來更像女性。他於2005年起，在歌謠搖滾樂隊「實驗台天竺鼠」擔任主音歌手，穿女裝的契機是2011年時，有雜誌的女模特兒突然缺席，結果被拜託頂替。從此之後，即使在舞台上表演，他亦如覺醒般一直男扮女裝。更令人難以置信的是，谷琢磨於2015年更新駕照，竟順利以女裝照片通過，獲得「國家承認」。 <br />\n<br />\n不少網民得悉谷琢磨背後的「真相」後，不能相信事實如此「殘酷」，有人驚呼「怎麼可能是40歲的大叔！」，亦有人留言表示「皮膚比20多歲的我還要好！」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/173028_0ca04e9ad6959bac1c6e2209ba6a170c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F173028_0ca04e9ad6959bac1c6e2209ba6a170c.jpg&h=dcddb657&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/173030_5cb7934979e001aaa56f40663483834e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F173030_5cb7934979e001aaa56f40663483834e.jpg&h=d2d96da3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/173031_127d8ebdb5e39fe68248bc9b849cf287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F173031_127d8ebdb5e39fe68248bc9b849cf287.jpg&h=0b348f32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/173031_21a65dea8815d8ede245fd6fd56ddfde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F173031_21a65dea8815d8ede245fd6fd56ddfde.jpg&h=ae75db74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/173032_21a65dea8815d8ede245fd6fd56ddfde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F173032_21a65dea8815d8ede245fd6fd56ddfde.jpg&h=4d3c6cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/mobile/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171121%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001.html&d=Gh71wH31UTxdj3cGD%2F2x97DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=4d613b88\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171121/mobile/bknint-20171121052303715-1121_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌⋯ 以後j 女前 都要除褲驗正身先得⋯"},{"pid":"033e6e2016caf2346b2c173150fedc70e67cacd2","tid":478638,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"咁佢本身男生女相"},{"pid":"855f055a67211d4ce6a6c749176c50b295710e8a","tid":478638,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"You竟然是個爸"}]}